&lt;p&gt;Open the &lt;code&gt;ApiDbContext&lt;/code&gt; file, configure the mappings for the &lt;code&gt;CommandEntity&lt;/code&gt; and add a required one-to-many relation between this tables:&lt;/p&gt;
